::DrillBit::

DrillBit went to the computer, and located two empty rooms. He then
spoted GoldenEye and Dollen. He walked up to them.
"Hey. I'm supposed to get you two some rooms. We have two available. Do
you have any personal items, back at the ship, that you might need help
moveing in here?" He asked.
